text: Ice Lake is a small lake in Wallowa County, in northeastern Oregon, United States, in the Eagle Cap Wilderness region.http://www.statesmanjournal.com/story/travel/outdoors/2014/08/13/icy- plunge-punctuates-climb-matterhorn/13997947/ Its outflow is Adam Creek.http://www.bakercityherald.com/csp/mediapool/sites/BakerCityHerald/Opinion/story.csp?cid=4155591&sid;=820&fid;=151 ==See also== * List of lakes in Oregon == References == Category:Lakes of Oregon Category:Eagle Cap Wilderness
title: Ice Lake (Oregon)
